---
classes:
  - nginx::install
  - nginx::php_cgi
  - nginx::add_site

###! note: The nginx::add_site class and the nginx::del_site class cannot be used at the same time when they have the same name
### Configure nginx::add_site
nginx::add_site:
  name: <%= params['site_domain'] %>
  owner: <%= params['owner'] %>
  group: www-data
  root_directory: <%= params['site_directory'] %>